<h1>XMvn cookbook</h1>
<p>This is a cookbook for conversion of current <em>mvn-rpmbuild</em> spec file into <em>xmvn</em>
style spec file.</p>
<p>Available recipes are:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="alias.html">alias</a></li>
<li><a href="arguments.html">arguments</a></li>
<li><a href="debug.html">debug</a></li>
<li><a href="generic.html">generic</a></li>
<li><a href="package.html">package</a></li>
<li><a href="singleton.html">singleton</a></li>
<li><a href="skiptests.html">skiptests</a></li>
<li><a href="symlink.html">symlink</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Recipes by keyword:</p>
<ul>
<li><em>passing arguments to the maven</em>:
<a href="arguments.html">arguments</a></li>
<li><em>enabling debugging output</em>:
<a href="debug.html">debug</a></li>
<li><em>javadoc subpackage Requires</em>:
<a href="generic.html">generic</a></li>
<li><em>custom package layout</em>:
<a href="package.html">package</a></li>
<li><em>skip test compilation and execution</em>:
<a href="skiptests.html">skiptests</a></li>
<li><em>build section changes</em>:
<a href="generic.html">generic</a></li>
<li><em>compatibility symlinks</em>:
<a href="singleton.html">singleton</a>,
<a href="symlink.html">symlink</a></li>
<li><em>jpackage-utils BuildRequires</em>:
<a href="generic.html">generic</a></li>
<li><em>install section changes</em>:
<a href="generic.html">generic</a></li>
<li><em>artifact aliases</em>:
<a href="alias.html">alias</a>,
<a href="singleton.html">singleton</a></li>
<li><em>files section changes</em>:
<a href="generic.html">generic</a></li>
<li><em>maven BuildRequires</em>:
<a href="generic.html">generic</a></li>
<li><em>auto-requires</em>:
<a href="generic.html">generic</a></li>
<li><em>singleton packaging</em>:
<a href="singleton.html">singleton</a></li>
</ul>
